il the first paycheck, but the place where I work has a locker room and shower (hand wash laundry when no one&amp;#39;s around), so I&amp;#39;m able to keep up appearances in the meantime and have a small space under my desk to hideaway things I need to store.</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/109900201050670221/comments/default/4715676608725415362'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/109900201050670221/comments/default/4715676608725415362'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2004/10/employment.html?showComment=1395099353005#c4715676608725415362' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2004/10/employment.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-109900201050670221' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/posts/default/109900201050670221' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-947910795"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="4:35 PM"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-4466435611249546531</id><published>2014-01-22T16:17:35.817-08:00</published><updated>2014-01-22T16:17:35.817-08:00</updated><title type='text'>I&amp;#39;ve been going on interviews. I clean/patch m...</title><content type='html'>I&amp;#39;ve been going on interviews. I clean/patch myself up and give it my all.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The employer doesn&amp;#39;t need to know that I rode the subway all night.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Or that I brushed my teeth and washed my face in the McDonald&amp;#39;s across the street. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Or that I went over my scuffed 